visitors Package¶

Description¶

Visitors used to traverse the Clafer AST in order to ultimately generate a Z3Instance object.

Created on Mar 26, 2013

@author: ezulkosk

class visitors.CreateBracketedConstraints.CreateBracketedConstraints(z3)¶

Bases: visitors.VisitorTemplate.VisitorTemplate

Variables:
  • self.currentConstraint – (BracketedConstraint) Holds the constraint currently being traversed.
  • self.inConstraint – (bool) True if the traversal is currently within a constraint.
  • claferStack – ([ClaferSort]) Stack of clafers used primarily for debugging.
  • z3 – (Z3Instance) The Z3 solver.

Converts Clafer constraints to z3 syntax, adds constraints to z3.z3_constraints field.
